arts.ttl: RKC and PEC Zwolle end 2024 with a draw
arts.sum: The clash between RKC Waalwijk and PEC Zwolle ended in a 1-1 draw on Friday evening. After only ten minutes, RKC had the lead with Mohammed Ihattaren crossing for Oskar Zawada to head in at the near post.
